<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,287,1929,1951]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">FIGURE 11.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[295,613,1929,1951]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="gigas" status="sp. n." subGenus="Asiosphegina">
<emphasis box="[295,613,1929,1951]" italics="true" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Sphegina (Asiosphegina) gigas</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[621,679,1930,1951]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[621,679,1930,1951]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" rank="species">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
(A, B, paratype, C, D, E holotype). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1058,1083,1929,1950]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">A.</emphasis>
Posterior part of abdomen, lateral view; the unmodified pilosity omitted. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[548,571,1960,1981]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">B.</emphasis>
Sternite IV, ventral view; the unmodified pilosity omitted. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1174,1199,1960,1982]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">C.</emphasis>
Genitalia, lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,175,1991,2012]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">D.</emphasis>
Left surstylus, lateral view. 
